# The frontend fetches its OIDC configuration from GET /api/config at runtime.
# No VITE_ variables are needed — the backend reads these from its own env vars
# (AUTHENTIK_ISSUER_URI, AUTHENTIK_AUDIENCE, AUTHENTIK_REDIRECT_URI) and serves
# them to the browser, so the same Docker image works across environments.
#
# For local development, start the backend with those env vars set and the
# Vite proxy (/api → http://localhost:8080) will forward the config request.
